(1212, 229, 'description', '<ol>\r\n 	<li>The columns. slip-ways, car loading platforms adopt 5mm thickness steel plate with CNC machine to cut and bend in one time and then welded with square tubes. It has high structural strength and beautiful appearence.</li>\r\n 	<li>The hydraulic cylinder seals are all imported from Italy, and the quality is stable and reliable. The oil pipes are all made of double-layer steel mesh hoses, and the bursting pressure is greater than or equal to 100 MPa.</li>\r\n 	<li>The hydraulic system has its own pressure holding function. When the equipment rises to a specified position, the pressure is maintained in the 20MPa without unloading. In addition, the loading plate has a mechanical anti-fall mechanism and double anti-fall protection.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
